

 LS          -    This command will help list all the files and folders.

 Tuoch       -    This is use to create a file

 Mkdir       -    This command is use to create a folder

 Ls -al      -    This command is use to list all files and folders including hidden file in a long format

 cp          -    This is use to copy a file or folder

 mv          -    It is use to move a folder or file.

 rm          -    It is use to delete a file

 rm -f       -    This is to forcefully remove a folder with contents

 Cat         -    This command is use to see the contents of a file

 pwd        -    This command will show you your present directory.
